&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://dinersclubofferstool.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/LATAM-LIMA-MARAS-OFFER-LOGO-MEDIUM.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;alignnone size-full wp-image-4254&quot; src=&quot;http://dinersclubofferstool.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/LATAM-LIMA-MARAS-OFFER-LOGO-MEDIUM.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;LATAM- LIMA- MARAS- OFFER- LOGO MEDIUM&quot; width=&quot;75&quot; height=&quot;75&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
The cuisine of Chef Rafael Piqueras&rsquo; tasting menu takes diners on a culinary tour through the jungle, coast and mountains of Peru, filled with one surprise after another. Set in a contemporary dining room within the Westin Lima hotel, Maras was named &ldquo;Best New Restaurant 2012&rdquo; and &ldquo;Best Hotel Restaurant 2013&rdquo; by the Summum Culinary Guide, Peru&amp;#8217;s most reputable culinary awards.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Please book by online at &lt;a href=&quot;http://lima.restorando.com.pe/restaurante/maras-restaurante&quot;&gt;http://lima.restorando.com.pe/restaurante/maras-restaurante&lt;/a&gt; or contact Opera by phone at +51 1 201 5023&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Mention Diners Club International Privileges Dining Collection to receive your special benefit&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide your name, date you would like to dine, number of guests, preferred time, cell or local (hotel) phone number and email address&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Cancellation Policy &ndash; As a courtesy Maras asks for 24 hour cancelation notice&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;TERMS &amp;amp; CONDITIONS&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Must use your Diners Club Card for payment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Menu is priced at 180 soles but may change due to market availability and prices, to be confirmed at the time of booking)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Follow booking instructions to ensure receiving your Privileges Dining Collection amenity&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Preferred bookings based on Availability at the time of booking&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Private kitchen tour is based on availability of chef and restaurants capacity at time of reservation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Your Privileges Dining Collection benefit may not be combined with other offers&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Fulfillment of the offer is the sole responsibility of the participating Diners Club International Restaurant Merchant&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Restaurant participation and benefits are subject to change or cancellation without notice&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

